          <title>Royals agree with RHP Carlos Est&#233;vez on 2-year, $22M deal, person familiar with deal tells AP</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Royals and reliever Carlos Estévez have agreed to a two-year, $22 million contract, a person familiar with the deal told The Associated Press on Wednesday night.]]></description>
