        <item>
          <title>Man City rallies to beat Club Brugge and advance in Champions League. PSG also wins and stays in</title>
          <description><![CDATA[GENEVA (AP) — Manchester City stayed in the Champions League, barely. Paris Saint-Germain saved its elite status in style. Both had risked embarrassing exits before winning on Wednesday, grateful to be among the 24 teams in the knockout stage.]]></description>
